title: Or What

description.plain:
Or What is a song by 41 & NLE Choppa that was teased by 41 rapper Kyle Richh on Instagram Live showing 4100 gang members, NLE Choppa and others getting sturdy to the slow, seductive jersey drill beat.

The song was met with criticism after NLE Choppa made a song with OY rapper and Harlem Native, DD Osama with “O Let’s Do It (Remix)” feat. Dee Play4Keeps of whom is an opp of 41. On top of this, one of NLE’s lyrics are “Notti Bop and you will get popped, like a hair stylist, hit his dreadlocks”
And people believed tension grew when DD posted cryptic messages on his IG stories and unfollowed Choppa.

The song released on Friday, September 6th, 2024.
